        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Testing a live computer-use agent against a real desktop is slow and non-deterministic. The practical approach is to decouple the action dispatcher from the model loop and mock it in tests. Record the model's action sequence for a reference task, then assert the sequence is reproduced correctly when the same screenshots are fed in."
          }
